  {
    "hotel_id": "6595957",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/tokyo-cubo/hotel/bandung-id.html",
    "name": "Tokyo Cubo",
    "detail": "Tokyo Cubo is excellent for the value of money. The place itself is very close to the station (only 800m or about 15-20minutes of walking to get there) near the heart of Bandung so if you plan your day to get started from the center of Bandung, it's location is really helping. The staff is also really nice, very clean, you get towels, hot water for shower and for toilet necessity; there's soap--no shampoo though. The downside is no fridge in the common room at all so you can't really save any easy to stale food--the staff are willing to help though, they help me put down my yogurt in the cafe next door. The room can get really freezing but there's nothing you could do because it's a shared room, the other occupants may find it hot if you lower the ac so if you're not fond of cold that much (like me) you might want to bring extra blanket yourself. Wifi is nice, there's no breakfast included but there's a lot of food stall in front of the hostel. Thanks Tokyo cubo!",
